products.title: Luxari PVC Blackout Beige Electric Roller Blind
products.metadescription: Luxari pvc blackout beige electric roller blind in cream. Made to measure from 153.92 with free uk mainland delivery. This electric roller blind includes 5-year guarantee and child safety features.
products.productdescription:
Their luxari pvc blackout range is available in classic colours and is ideal for damp rooms or areas that are exposed to heat. 
 
This beige roller blind is made from a pvc fabric so is therefore waterproof and flame retardant - perfect for kitchens and bathrooms! 
 
 Product id: db-erbx1511 fabric colour: beige material: fiberglass core laminated with pvc layered coating lining: colour match backing - see sample headrail: durable aluminium roller tube supported by white steel brackets - top, face or side fix   control type: electric control battery powered energy saving rating: er3 - highest energy saving value - uv protection and effective thermal retention blackout: yes
